{"word":"H7802 - שׁוּשַׁן עֵדוּת - Shûwshan ʻÊdûwth - shoo-shan' ay-dooth' - Shoshannim-Eduth","slug":"H7802","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שׁוּשַׁן עֵדוּת</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Shûwshan ʻÊdûwth"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shoo-shan' ay-dooth'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Shoshannim-Eduth"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D5;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E0;&#x05BC;&#x05D9;&#x05DD; &#x05E2;&#x05D3;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05EA;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DF; &#x05E2;&#x05D3;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05EA; - shu&#x0302;shan &#x201B;e&#x0302;du&#x0302;th  sho&#x0302;shann&#x0131;&#x0302;ym &#x201B;e&#x0302;du&#x0302;th</b> - <i>shoo-shan' or sho-shan-neem' (ay-dooth')</i><p/>The second form being plural; from <a href=\"#/H7799\">H7799</a> and <a href=\"#/H5715\">H5715</a>; <i>lily</i> (or <i>trumpet</i>) <i>of assemblage</i>; <i>Shushan Eduth</i> or <i>Shoshannim Eduth</i>, the title of a popular song: - Shoshannim-Eduth, Shushan-eduth."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7791\">H7791</a>, <a href=\"#/H7793\">H7793</a>, <a href=\"#/H7794\">H7794</a>, <a href=\"#/H7799\">H7799</a>, <a href=\"#/H7800\">H7800</a>, <a href=\"#/H7803\">H7803</a>, <a href=\"#/H8284\">H8284</a>, <a href=\"#/H8364\">H8364</a>"}]}